{"tid":141910,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[伏已中] 國際轉運唔見幾千蚊貨，追咗三個幾月。客服愛理不理","createTime":"2017-03-03T10:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T07:08:13.000Z","uid":33325,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d1fa4975ba59cbc61c2c3fdac491c6c4d942fcd5","tid":141910,"uid":33325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T10:12:08.000Z","msg":"利申：借Friend A/C, 圖後補<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，上年年尾Black Friday買咗幾件褸送咗去集運嘅Oregon倉，當地速遞顯示已簽收。<br />\n但自己用果間轉運公司就遲遲未有record<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。咁諗住peak season會佢地會比較忙，諗住等多兩三個禮拜先再再check下個status啦咁。<br />\n點知過咗成個月都未有update，就打上去CS，點知打十幾次冇人聽電話。打多好多次之後終於有人聽佢又話國際轉運係第二個部門，要我whatsapp佢比嘅電話號碼咁, 但係whatsapp就一路都無覆。<br />\n咁我就梗喺再打上去啦（都喺打幾十次先聽），佢又話入倉搵下先，會再覆我。如是者幾次都冇覆。之後有次又話搵到D貨， 話會update返記錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n咁之後就真係有update到其中一件貨記錄話到左美國 (但明明果日佢係電話話係倉見到件貨)，但其他貨就話未簽收（當地速遞明明已經話有人簽收）。再打上去CS佢又話其他未簽收嘅貨其實喺唔見咗，話會賠錢，叫我send返d單比佢哋, 但係send咗比佢哋又冇晒影。#kill1#<br />\n終於前幾日whatsapp又覆話客服轉咗人，依家會有新人幫我follow up。點知又喺比另外一個冇人應機嘅number我。終於頂唔順send mail 去消委會cap圖send比佢，點知佢話&quot;唯有喺咁啦～我都唔識攪&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家唔見左嘅就唔見左啦, 咁未唔見果件究竟去左邊?<br />\n依家即係咁:<br />\n1.\t有一件貨唔見咗＞話會賠＞冇影<br />\n2.\t另外一件貨有記錄喺美國倉，但又話依家冇做國際轉運&gt;都喺冇影<br />\n奉勸各連登巴絲以後網購選擇集運公司要小心"},{"pid":"f42a37580f2d7036c9c060c178d2a56c35213812","tid":141910,"uid":34661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T11:16:34.000Z","msg":"唉，我果間咪又係一樣<br />\n屌你老味有就有無就無，都唔知拖乜撚野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：用緊T字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79fb252097d01826275d80344d092a9f87a0734c","tid":141910,"uid":13645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T11:18:02.000Z","msg":"trans?"},{"pid":"f858e6c7668579790347e25eafe64a310318a2f5","tid":141910,"uid":40950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T11:22:45.000Z","msg":"開名啦<br />\n如實直說，怕佢有牙咩"},{"pid":"e840b15035153056beda2a342da5893cd57e32b1","tid":141910,"uid":33325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T11:54:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2993hZ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2993hZ2.jpg&h=454629e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/03/195341_599738ee71c8e83b9869eea353ac0d9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F03%2F195341_599738ee71c8e83b9869eea353ac0d9e.jpg&h=6501c047&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/03/195342_5eeb9e536673afb85ee8b167f9b6df6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F03%2F195342_5eeb9e536673afb85ee8b167f9b6df6d.jpg&h=774f7752&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/74m0W8t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F74m0W8t.jpg&h=24c99b7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cUB6FC7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcUB6FC7.jpg&h=56932039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5971522.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5971522.jpg&h=3a87c7b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/03/195400_6a456dd49e58712bb2bb0edc211810d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F03%2F195400_6a456dd49e58712bb2bb0edc211810d0.jpg&h=48878de1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NM9v4H3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNM9v4H3.jpg&h=b53aa49a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/73056p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F73056p4.jpg&h=f8cb663a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/03/195404_ed56e55cd66bbde270a223f4ee2c25aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F03%2F195404_ed56e55cd66bbde270a223f4ee2c25aa.jpg&h=0a31303d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/03/195421_1b6c834ed5d02a62d17f3737f1ac0250.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F03%2F195421_1b6c834ed5d02a62d17f3737f1ac0250.jpg&h=c6ad9439&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28xy627.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28xy627.jpg&h=0f77d1b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/282sG6A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F282sG6A.jpg&h=19d4f118&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"746d99aeda360c5360effe53fdc3d71b0ab32030","tid":141910,"uid":33325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T11:56:28.000Z","msg":"催咗三個幾月得個吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c46a987185959737393b915227d5f5c466f209","tid":141910,"uid":34661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:19:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>催咗三個幾月得個吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌，真係T_PLINK<br />\n佢個電話唔係無人聽就係灑尻你<br />\n<br />\n係咪報警都無用？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc3ae3c9885bbd61eeafa8970228a7c327e7641","tid":141910,"uid":26224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:33:50.000Z","msg":"用開 us-ex. 都試過唔見貨, 但睇 tracking information 又話送左。<br />\n好彩上網揾到個簽名係另一間大陸集運，應該係送錯左倉<br />\n立刻去果間大陸集運開 account 同登記件貨，最後運埋香港，但好貴運費。<br />\n同一時間我又同件貨商店報失， 佢又無條件送個件。<br />\n最後收左二件貨。袋左過千蚊"},{"pid":"99e826b014a847dd4b02a0a9ff35506323e2f7d1","tid":141910,"uid":33325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80cfda45356ea39803d8993b6610b37fff8b8e56","tid":141910,"uid":68152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:33:04.000Z","msg":"有無試過同 seller 溝通下，同佢講無收到件，叫佢 refund 返比你啊？<br />\n<br />\n就算果個 tracking 比人簽收左，都可以係送錯地址比人簽收左？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我之前都有試過類似既事，我用果間代運公司一直話無收到無收到，但明明係簽收左，佢叫我聯絡返 seller , 教左我點同 seller 溝通，果時個 cs 講得好詳細下！<br />\n(原本我都覺果間公司好次好不付責任，&quot;不過原本收件方係無權限要求簽收紀錄 同 送件地址&quot;），所以佢地就算無收到件都好，都證明唔到，只可能要我聯絡返 seller , seller 再聯絡速遞 check，最後原來真係速遞送錯地址<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以當下 seller 就很 refund 返比我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你證明到送錯地址 或者 果個簽收人唔係你，佢都會退返錢比你架！<br />\n同埋唔好比個 seller 知，你用集運公司，唔見見無得賠架好次！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n或者可以同係信用卡公司講你無用卡買果個款項既蚊，叫佢唔好比佢過數。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14df990f28048b41c29b2ec8bd1d7769b2fa64cd","tid":141910,"uid":68152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:34:21.000Z","msg":"用著間咁既，cs 一 d 都幫唔到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好L 慘"},{"pid":"c00117d7bb2371a257c9efa0b9395d4d73df9d4b","tid":141910,"uid":53378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:37:14.000Z","msg":"雙11爆倉爆到仆街之後無用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e12542dcb9067ca48585add6a021aff164a4a6","tid":141910,"uid":35716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:38:40.000Z","msg":"T_PLINK 之前果班好好服務的巴打CS走哂......<br />\n而家好似直接由佢母公司運通管理..."},{"pid":"c087dbcfa815ccfe860a39a6cc2ab9f9cc373d2d","tid":141910,"uid":68152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:42:19.000Z","msg":"Toplink(匯購八方）集運苦主區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t